  <brief_title>Outcome of Patients After Total Knee Replacement: A Comparison of Femoral Nerve Block and Epidural Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Outcome of Patients After Total Knee Replacement: A Comparison of Femoral Nerve Block and Epidural Anesthesia. A Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
